consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"title":"addAnnotation:","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The options to use when creating images with the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"title":"MLNPointCollection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances, and the line segments that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}]}}}